<task id="task_3B5EAB62FC654E5086EB4FA65BD8738B">
  <title>Place an Mbox Around a Table Cell</title>
  <shortdesc>You can place an mbox around a single table cell. 
  </shortdesc>
  <prolog>
    <metadata>
      <othermeta name="solution" content="Target" />
      <othermeta name="topic" content="Advanced" />
    </metadata>
  </prolog>
  <taskbody>
    <steps id="steps_B57B3EF5F3E04F2698C8402E90236495">
      <step id="step_FED796A374464F91BC1DDE2EDFCC93AE">
        <cmd>Ensure the page includes a 
			 <xref href="t_Referencing_mboxjs.xml#task_4A321498EDAF4A048E3B9A74FD9E67E9" type="task" format="dita" scope="local">reference to 
				<filepath>mbox.js</filepath></xref> in the header. 
		  </cmd>
      </step>
      <step id="step_5E162607D117473DB7DD3B97E9A4EB7F">
        <cmd>Insert mbox default around the cell, not outside the cell. 
		  </cmd>
      </step>
      <step id="step_3A3894F160E04222BFB5DB971C71E33C">
        <cmd>Immediately follow the default content close<codeph>
				&lt;/div&gt;</codeph> with the<codeph> mboxCreate</codeph> function. 
		  </cmd>
        <stepresult>
          <p>Give the mbox a unique name which makes sense for your campaign
				strategy and company procedures. In the example below, the mbox is named
				myMbox. 
			 </p>
          <p>Example of mbox around a cell: 
			 </p>
          <p>
            <table id="table_939AA5551950413385F11BBF52837DDD">
              <tgroup cols="2">
                <colspec colnum="1" colname="col1" colwidth="*" />
                <colspec colnum="2" colname="col2" colwidth="*" />
                <thead>
                  <row>
                    <entry colname="col1">Before 
						</entry>
                    <entry colname="col2">After 
						</entry>
                  </row>
                </thead>
                <tbody>
                  <row>
                    <entry colname="col1">
                      <p>
                        <codeblock outputclass="syntax html">&lt;table&gt;

&lt;tr&gt;

&lt;td&gt;Peaches&lt;/td&gt;

&lt;td&gt;Cherries&lt;/td&gt;

&lt;/tr&gt;

&lt;tr&gt;

&lt;td&gt;Walnuts&lt;/td&gt;

&lt;td&gt;Almonds&lt;/td&gt;

&lt;/tr&gt;

&lt;/table&gt; </codeblock>
                      </p>
                    </entry>
                    <entry colname="col2">
                      <p>
                        <codeblock outputclass="syntax html">&lt;table&gt;
  
&lt;tr&gt;

&lt;td&gt;

&lt;div class="mboxDefault"&gt;

Peaches

&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;script type="text/javascript"&gt;

mboxCreate('myMbox');

&lt;/script&gt;

&lt;/td&gt;

&lt;td&gt;Cherries&lt;/td&gt;

&lt;/tr&gt;

&lt;tr&gt;

&lt;td&gt;Walnuts&lt;/td&gt;

&lt;td&gt;Almonds&lt;/td&gt;

&lt;/tr&gt;

&lt;/table&gt; </codeblock>
                      </p>
                    </entry>
                  </row>
                  <row>
                    <entry colname="col1"></entry>
                    <entry colname="col2"></entry>
                  </row>
                </tbody>
              </tgroup>
            </table>
          </p>
        </stepresult>
      </step>
      <step id="step_875AFB13B66C40A6ABE25F6AA0ED52CA">
        <cmd>
          <xref href="t_Validating_an_Mbox.xml#task_4BB8E090CBBF4C56A39BB63BF1ADB964" type="task" format="dita" scope="local">Validate the mbox</xref>. 
		  </cmd>
      </step>
    </steps>
  </taskbody>
